# -------------------------------
# PSD / College RPP Commit Template
# -------------------------------

# TYPE: feat | fix | refactor | data | docs | chore
# STEP: 01-merge | 02-missing | 03-clean | 04-merge | other

<type>: (<step>) <short summary>

# Why is this change needed?
# (bug fix, new feature, data update, etc.)

# What changed?
# - bullet points of key changes

# Data impact (if applicable):
# - affects cohorts? flags? outputs?

# Notes / follow-ups:
# - anything to revisit later

# -------------------------------
# Remove comments before committing
# -------------------------------